<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<time_sig>8.7.8.7. with Refrain 8.7.8.7</time_sig>
<title>Ʋba pin Chitokaka yʋt ƲIT21</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba pin Chitokaka yʋt,
 &quot;Oh ile kostininchi,&quot;
 Et pim ahanchi pulla ka
 Eho haklo pullashke.

[C1]
   Hatak yoshoba pia hʋt
   Pin Chisʋs achukma ka
   Il i̱ nukkilla hinla cho?
   Anukfillit ke pisa.

[V2]
 2 Yoshoba bieka hocha
 Aiokpuloka fehna
 E chukowa̱ hosi hona,
 Pi̱ nukha̱klo tok oke.

[C2]
   Hatak yoshoba pia hʋt
   Pin Chisʋs achukma ka
   Il i̱ nukkilla hinla cho?
   Anukfillit ke pisa.

[V3]
 Kʋna kia pi̱ nukha̱klot
 Pi okchalincha hi ʋt
 Iksho; Chisʋs ak bano tok:
 Eho holitoblashke.

[C3]
   Hatak yoshoba pia hʋt
   Pin Chisʋs achukma ka
   Il i̱ nukkilla hinla cho?
   Anukfillit ke pisa.

[V4]
 Il ile kostininchi cha,
 Pi okcha̱ya he mak o̱,
 Im issish hanta fehna ka
 Isht pi chumpa tok oke.

[C4]
   Hatak yoshoba pia hʋt
   Pin Chisʋs achukma ka
   Il i̱ nukkilla hinla cho?
   Anukfillit ke pisa.

[V5]
 Ʋba aiasha achukma
 Ont pim atahli tuk osh,
 &quot;Ho minti, hatak puta ma!&quot;
 Et pim ahanchi hoke.

[C5]
   Hatak yoshoba pia hʋt
   Pin Chisʋs achukma ka
   Il i̱ nukkilla hinla cho?
   Anukfillit ke pisa.</lyrics>
<aka>&quot;Sinners, can you hate the Saviour?&quot;</aka>
</song>